Recently saw Pushpa 2 reloaded version Jan 21st  2025 and there was no Ac working ..There were No staff member to be seen at all … no food was kept at the interval …and no body was there at the food counter.The  staff member later was seen at the Ross omlet shop working there as part time … The Quality of this place is gone down completely because of unprofessional staff members and no cleanliness maintained and No security at all as anyone was entering to use the toilet as a public toilet.This could lead  to criminal activities in the future.I am from Vasco and I want this place to improve.. please hire staff who is willing to work professionally and maintain this place.

It's small and very cosy, like your personal sitting room, seats are super comfy especially at LUXE where you get nice recliner. screens are small so dnt book your seats far from screen. Ac was very chilling. They could improve on their eating menu though which doesn't have much to choose from
